<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">الدَّلِيل من الْمَعْقُول:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">لنا:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>زَالَت يَد الْوَدِيعَة فارتفع العقد؛ لِأَنَّهَا دخلت فِي ضَمَان الْمُودع وَصَارَت<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>